Note:
compiler/frontend/lexical/keywords.runa
Language Keyword Recognition and Management

This module provides comprehensive keyword functionality including:
- Natural language keyword recognition ("Let", "Process called", etc.)
- Technical syntax keyword support for --developer mode
- Multi-word keyword detection and validation
- Context-sensitive keyword classification
- Dual syntax mode keyword conversion
- Keyword precedence and disambiguation
- Integration with lexer for token classification
- Performance optimized keyword matching
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

Note: =====================================================================
Note: KEYWORD DATA STRUCTURES
Note: =====================================================================

Type called "KeywordMap":
    natural_keywords as Dictionary[String, String]
    technical_keywords as Dictionary[String, String]
    multi_word_keywords as Dictionary[String, List[String]]
    keyword_categories as Dictionary[String, String]
    precedence_levels as Dictionary[String, Integer]

Type called "KeywordRecognizer":
    recognizer_id as String
    keyword_map as KeywordMap
    current_mode as String
    statistics as Dictionary[String, Integer]

